OAuth implementation learnings

This website is useful for setting up Twitter/X OAuth:
https://docs.x.com/fundamentals/authentication/oauth-2-0/bearer-tokens

The prerequisite section is particularly useful.

OAuth app setup choices used:

- App permissions: Read and write
- App type: Web app
- Client type: Confidential client

For the app info fields, you need to use real-looking website values.

- Callback URL: localhost
- Website URL: make it hope
